                        <interp inst="t18400817-name-737" type="given" value="HENRY"></interp>HENRY JOHNSON</persName>
                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> I never saw that man before.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18400817-name-738" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18400817-name-738" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18400817-name-738" type="surname" value="JOHNSON"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18400817-name-738" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE JOHNSON</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a greengrocer; I was a policeman. I know the male prisoner—I was present when he was convicted—he is the per<lb></lb>son mentioned in this certificate, which I got from Mr. Clark's office.—(<hi rend="italic">read</hi>.)</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">W. BOYCE</hi>. Aged 40.—
